title: The LOST Now Thats Music - Oct.2016 (3-CD Deluxe)ak320
description:
The LOST Now Thats Music - Oct.2016 (3-CD Deluxe)ak320

The last one of these I posted was some time ago and I began building this but some  things were lost and this compilation was split up and not on the drive I expected. 
So it stayed lost until I switched out some HDD's and then it was found. 
But it was for last fall, it was the follow up to the Aug.- Sept. NTM .
So I did the tagging and numbering ect. Editing and I added the 3rd disk as a bonus and to kinda bring it up to semi current but since no one else really shares what I do I find it to be relevant and timely and it kicks ass(the important part).

I have slowed my roll as Im sure at leat 1 or 2 of ya out there may have noticed and Im really close to shutting it down. Im sick of numbers whores and uploaders who dont care about the share only the numbers. If you dont love it dont up it. And other shit that I deal with, equipment, trolls,sites going under, peeps leaving,The real worlds shit ugh. It all adds up, But enough heres why Im here now...
